POE-Component-Client-Stomp-Utils version 0.02
=============================================

This module is for making life with Stomp somewhat easier. It does the boring
job of creating Stomp frames. It works basically the same as Net::Stomp but is
for the POE environment instead.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

Net::Stomp::Frame

